{"calories":"960","carbs":100,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"\u003cp\u003eChef Shanna is sharing the love with creamy, cheesy grits—basically a warm hug in a bowl. The grits are a luxurious bed for perfectly roasted parsnips, carrots, mushrooms, and broccolini, all tossed in sage and thyme butter. Add toasted almonds for crunch and you\u0026#x27;ve got a colorful, comforting bowl everyone will enjoy.\u003c/p\u003e","difficulty":"medium","external_id":"d3280b19b1","fat":54,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55837/1pPlJAvTR0m2QciCwIEP_Roasted_Fall_Vegetables_with_Creamy_Parmesan_Grits_and_Herb_Butter_FF-0110___HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55837/hero_1pPlJAvTR0m2QciCwIEP_Roasted_Fall_Vegetables_with_Creamy_Parmesan_Grits_and_Herb_Butter_FF-0110___HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55837/menu_small_1pPlJAvTR0m2QciCwIEP_Roasted_Fall_Vegetables_with_Creamy_Parmesan_Grits_and_Herb_Butter_FF-0110___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55837/small_square_1pPlJAvTR0m2QciCwIEP_Roasted_Fall_Vegetables_with_Creamy_Parmesan_Grits_and_Herb_Butter_FF-0110___HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55837/medium_square_1pPlJAvTR0m2QciCwIEP_Roasted_Fall_Vegetables_with_Creamy_Parmesan_Grits_and_Herb_Butter_FF-0110___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55837/recipe_profile_page_1pPlJAvTR0m2QciCwIEP_Roasted_Fall_Vege