lavor as they roast, but won\u0026#x27;t be pleasant to bite into. We recommend discarding them before adding the herb butter. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eUse the remaining mascarpone as a spread for toast or a dip for fruit. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe recommend rinsing the pot from the grits ASAP to make cleanup easier. Cooled grits can be a tough scrub!\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["6\" small pot with lid","baking sheet"],"id":5704,"ingredients":["unsalted butter","cremini mushrooms","broccolini","carrots","parsnips","lemon","red onion","slivered almonds","quick-cooking grits","grated Parmesan cheese","mascarpone cheese","thyme","sage","chives"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"unsalted butter","quantity":"3.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2371/medium_square_medium_square_butter-test.jpg"},{"name":"cremini mushrooms","quantity":"6.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/326/medium_square_cremini-mushrooms-test2.jpg"},{"name":"broccolini","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/558/medium_square_BROCCOLINI_-4563_copy.jpg"},{"name":"carrots","quantity":"6.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/98/medium_square_CARROTS_-4424_copy.jpg"},{"name":"parsnips","quantity":"6.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2298/medium_square_parsnip.jpg"},{"name":"lemon","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/16/medium_square_LEMON_SLICED_1_copy.jpg"},{"name":"red onion","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/90/medium_square_red-onion-cut-half.jpg"},{"name":"slivered almonds","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/110/medium_square_Slivered_Almonds.jpg"},{"name":"quick-cooking grits","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2024/medium_square_grain-grits.jpg"},{"name":"grated Parmesan cheese","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2309/medium_square_parmesan-cheese-2.jpg"},{"name":"mascarpone cheese","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1501/medium_square_MASCARPONE_CHEESE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"thyme","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1289/medium_square_medium_square_herb-thyme-fresh.jpg"},{"name":"sage","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1277/medium_square_medium_square_sage-2.jpg"},{"name":"chives","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1281/medium_square_medium_square_chives-2-test.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":15,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":16,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":17,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55859/recipe_card_size_pOuJMFfKRVC8M8AjCqP2_1._Prepare_Ingredients.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 450°F. Unwrap \u003cstrong\u003ebutter\u003c/strong\u003e, place in a small bowl, and set aside to soften at room temperature. Wipe \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e clean with a damp paper towel and cut into .25-inch slices. Rinse remaining produce. Trim and discard woody bottoms of \u003cstrong\u003ebroccolini\u003c/strong\u003e, then cut crosswise into 2-inch pieces. Halve \u003cstrong\u003ecarrots\u003c/strong\u003e lengthwise. Quarter \u003cstrong\u003eparsnips\u003c/strong\u003e lengthwise. Halve \u003cstrong\u003elemon\u003c/strong\u003e. Peel \u003cstrong\u003eonion\u003c/strong\u003e, quarter, and separate layers.  \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Roast vegetables","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55860/recipe_card_size_LdNDhDUiSViYLPahI2iY_2._Roast_Vegetables_2X_3X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePick \u003cstrong\u003esage\u003c/strong\u003e leaves, discarding stems. On a baking sheet, toss \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003ebroccolini\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003ecarrots\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eparsnips\u003c/strong\u003e, and\u003cstrong\u003e onion \u003c/strong\u003ewith \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of whole thyme sprigs\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of sage\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e1.5 tablespoons olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003epepper \u003c/strong\u003eas desired (reserve remaining herbs for Step 4). Arrange in a single layer and roast, stirring halfway through, until tender and slightly charred, 20-22 minutes total. \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Toast almonds and cook grits","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55861/recipe_card_size_pqFOe8aQT2yHfUBv6L90_3._Toast_Almonds_and_Cook_Grits_2X_3X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile vegetables roast, heat \u003cstrong\u003e1 teaspoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e in a small pot over medium heat. When oil is shimmering, add \u003cstrong\u003ealmonds\u003c/strong\u003e and toast until light golden, 3-4 minutes. Transfer to a plate. Wipe pot clean; add \u003cstrong\u003e4 cups water\u003c/strong\u003e and bring to a boil over high heat. Whisk in \u003cstrong\u003egrits\u003c/strong\u003e and\u003cstrong\u003e .5 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e until smooth. Reduce heat to medium low and cover pot. Cook \u003cstrong\u003egrits\u003c/strong\u003e, whisking occasionally, until thickened, 5-7 minutes (a friend can do this part).  \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Make herb butter","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55862/recipe_card_size_Oe6E7Q9wSDah2hL0Nf6j_4._Make_Herb_Butter.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile grits cook, thinly slice \u003cstrong\u003echives\u003c/strong\u003e. Finely chop \u003cstrong\u003eremaining sage\u003c/strong\u003e leaves. Strip and finely chop leaves from \u003cstrong\u003eremaining thyme\u003c/strong\u003e, discarding stems. To bowl with softened butter, add \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of chives\u003c/strong\u003e (reserve remainder for grits), \u003cstrong\u003echopped\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003esage\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003echopped\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003ethyme\u003c/strong\u003e; using a fork, mash to combine—another great task for a friend.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Finish vegetables and grits","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55863/recipe_card_size_A0VcVpyAR7meMuKbmq02_5._Finish_Vegetables_2X_3X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eOnce roasted, remove and discard \u003cstrong\u003ewhole thyme sprigs\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003esage\u003c/strong\u003e leaves from vegetables (see recipe tip). Add \u003cstrong\u003e1 squeeze lemon juice\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003eherb butter \u003c/strong\u003eto roasted vegetables on sheet and toss to coat (use remaining lemon to brighten a glass of water). Once grits are thickened, remove pot from heat and whisk in \u003cstrong\u003eParmesan\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e3 tablespoons\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003emascarpone\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eremaining chives\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired (see recipe tip). \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Plate vegetables and grits","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/55864/recipe_card_size_NKi0WRugTaeyw8JXttnA_6._Plate.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eDivide \u003cstrong\u003eParmesan\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003egrits\u003c/strong\u003e between serving bowls (see recipe tip), then top with \u003cstrong\u003eroasted fall vegetables\u003c/strong\u003e. Garnish with \u003cstrong\u003etoasted\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003ealmonds \u003c/strong\u003eand dig in!\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Family-friendly","slug":"family-friendly","hex_color":""},{"name":"Quick cook","slug":"quick cook","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""},{"name":"Tree Nuts","slug":"tree nuts","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Loose Grain","slug":"loose-grain","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Family-friendly","slug":"family-friendly","hex_color":""},{"name":"Quick cook","slug":"quick cook","hex_color":""}],"feature":[]}}